nter; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Su co tran Chelsea vs West Ham Fan nem do choi nguoi lon hinh anh\" title=\"S\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham Fan n\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u01a1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/chelsea1-3245-1523327225.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Thibaut Courtois b\u1ecb Chicharito h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u1edf ph\u00fat 73. \u1ea2nh: Sun.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Azpillicueta \u1edf ph\u00fat 36. Gi\u1eefa hi\u1ec7p hai, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a MU, Chicharito Javier Hernandez ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a ch\u1ec9 ba ph\u00fat sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 cho West Ham. Qu\u00e1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch san b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Chicharito, m\u1ed9t fan West Ham n\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u01a1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn c\u00f3 h\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eadt v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, The Blues v\u1eabn x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 v\u1edbi 57 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n West Ham x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 14. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Conte ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 ba chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m. Nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italy s\u1ebd ra \u0111i v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c MU 2-3 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 32 h\u00f4m 7/4, Man City v\u1eabn v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng \u1edf ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n hai tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng trong 6 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Guardiola s\u1ebd \u0111\u0103ng quang \u1edf Premier League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, tham v\u1ecdng \u1edf Champions League c\u1ee7a Man City b\u1ecb d\u1ed9i g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh sau khi th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. R\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng 11/4, hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1.</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1048","checkdouble":"184023"},{"date":"15:09 11/04","title":"B\u1ea1n g\u00e1i Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 anti-fan","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/ban-gai-ronaldo-dap-tra-antifan.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeA