,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>PSG mua N'Golo Kante, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Thomas Tuchel, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n l\u00e0 t\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thomas Tuchel s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a PSG</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi\u1ebfn BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Tuchel muon PSG mua NGolo Kante hinh anh\" title=\"Thomas Tuchel mu\u1ed1n PSG mua NGolo Kante h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/2/13/Thomas-Tuchel-muon-PSG-mua-NGolo-Kante-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Tuchel \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1eafp d\u1eabn d\u1eaft PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nPSG \u0111\u00e3 chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao kh\u1ee7ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe. B\u1edfi v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u khi\u1ebfn BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi thay Unai Emery, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Thomas Tuchel. C\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Dortmund ch\u01b0a d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00eda Bayern Munich kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/thomas-tuchel-da-tim-duoc-ben-do-moi-184-183297.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Thomas Tuchel \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi</strong></span>. Theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi \u00f4ng n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, Tuchel \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Thomas Tuchel mu\u1ed1n PSG mua N'Golo Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Thomas Tuchel, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. PSG mua Kante, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Tuchel, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n l\u00e0 t\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"n\" golo=\"\" title=\"n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/16/conte-toi-chang-biet-kante-la-ai-khi-ve-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tuchel mu\u1ed1n PSG mua N'golo Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n Kante, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/psg-104.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>PSG</strong></span> ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u00e0 The Blues ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129. Ngo\u00e0i ra PSG c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi m\u1eddi h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn t\u1eeb PSG anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a N'Golo Kante \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/234148-40942/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a N'Golo Kante \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1040","checkdouble":"184021"},{"date":"14:09 11/04","title":"Thua \u0111au Liverpool, Silva \u0111\u00f2i \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng VAR \u1edf Champions League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/thua-dau-liverpool-silva-doi-ap-dung-var-o-champions-league