rdiola ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi The Citizens r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm khi Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Liverpool ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 2-0 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i x\u1eed l\u00fd ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/tranh-cai-tran-man-city-12-liverpool-leroy-sane-da-viet-vi-hay-chua-184-183975.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span> nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb. \u0110o\u1ea1n b\u0103ng quay ch\u1eadm sau \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y James Milner \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n Sane. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 bi\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb Sane th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p hai, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i. Hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Salah v\u00e0 Firmino gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Klopp ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Etihad.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thua dau Liverpool, Silva doi ap dung VAR o Champions League hinh anh\" title=\"Thua \u0111au Liverpool, Silva \u0111\u00f2i \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng VAR \u1edf Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/thua-dau-liverpool-silva-doi-ap-dung-var-o-champions-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bernardo Silva \u0111\u00f2i \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng VAR\u00a0\u1edf Champions League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Bernardo Silva k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/bi-loai-xung-dang-khoi-c1-pep-van-trut-gian-len-trong-tai-184-183980.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Mateu Lahoz</span> v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i l\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i trong hi\u1ec7p hai. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Bernardo Silva c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha cho bi\u1ebft: <em>\u201cC\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n v\u00ec b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-da-danh-bai-doi-bong-manh-nhat-the-gioi-184-184004.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/liverpool-da-danh-bai-doi-bong-manh-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-da-danh-bai-doi-bong-manh-nhat-the-gioi-184-184004.html\">Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span><br>\r\n<span>Sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Man City 2-1, HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u Champions c\u00f9ng CLB Roma.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u0103m sau, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n. Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Liverpool v\u00e0 ch\u00fac h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p may m\u1eafn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1edf Premier League v\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00e1i b\u00fat: T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Champions League n\u00ean b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd n\u00f3 s\u1ebd h\u1eefu \u00edch trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</em><strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tieu-diet-man-city-salah-lai-duoc-so-sanh-voi-messi-184-184005.html\">Ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Man City, Salah l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/gabriel-jesus-man-city-da-khoi-dau-tot-nhung-184-183996.html\">Gabriel Jesus: Man City \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate