opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Juventus, Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Di Stefano &ndash; huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n qua, Cristiano Ronaldo chi\u1ebfm m\u1ecdi ti\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juventus. Trong \u0111\u00f3, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ng\u1ea3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e8n, khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Buffon tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eafc d\u0129 trong khung th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111\u00e3 so s\u00e1nh Ronaldo v\u1edbi Di Stefano &ndash; huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i gi\u00e0nh 5 Champions League c\u00f9ng Real Madrid, v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 308 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 396 tr\u1eadn (giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 1953-1964).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 trong tay, HLV Zidane cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo th\u00ec s\u1ebd th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec Real \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Di Stefano\" title=\"Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/cac-cdv-se-yeu-quy-ronaldo-nhu-di-stefano.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Di Stefano</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Di Stefano, t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng, c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u0169ng s\u1ebd nh\u1edb Cristiano Ronaldo nh\u01b0 v\u1eady sau n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang &lsquo;t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng&rsquo; nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, Real Madrid \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp theo tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u Serie A c\u00f3 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n La Liga, Zidane cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1eady, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Juve, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i, b\u1edfi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Barcelona &ndash; CLB \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng La Liga. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 sao, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Di Stefano b\u1edfi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/real-madrid-vs-juventus-01h45-ngay-124-cop-chet-de-da-184-183999.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/real-madrid-vs-juventus-01h45-ngay-124-cop-chet-de-da.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/real-madrid-vs-juventus-01h45-ngay-124-cop-chet-de-da-184-183999.html\">Real Madrid vs Juventus (01h45 ng\u00e0y 12/4): C\u1ecdp ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 da</span><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Ronaldo ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n trong tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tan-man/cristiano-ronaldo-lap-cu-dup-vao-luoi-juve-hay-tham-vong-mot-cach-nghiem-tuc-392-183526.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/4/cristiano-ronaldo-lap-cu-dup-vao-luoi-juve-hay-tham-vong-mot-cach-nghiem-tuc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tan-man/cristiano-ronaldo-lap-cu-dup-vao-luoi-juve-hay-tham-vong-mot-cach-nghiem-tuc-392-183526.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juve: H\u00e3y tham v\u1ecdng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nghi\u00eam t\u00fac!</span><br>\r\nRonaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i nghi ng\u1edd. M\u1ecdi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng, l\u1eddi n\u00f3i c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t con ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd tho\u1ea3 m\u00e3n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1038","checkdouble":"184024"},{"date":"14:40 11/04","title":"T\u1ea1i sao Mourinho kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng Martial?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url