7n b\u1ecb l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Man United. Ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho si\u00eau sao Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0nh, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y Martial c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t n\u1ed5i Marcus Rashford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-martial-tu-choi-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-mu-172-180749.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Man United \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef Martial</span> \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Ph\u00eda Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u01b0\u1edfng h\u1eadu h\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Martial \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i k\u1ef3 v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 cung c\u1ea5p cho anh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tai sao Mourinho khong trong dung Martial hinh anh\" title=\"T\u1ea1i sao Mourinho kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/2/tai-sao-mourinho-khong-con-trong-dung-martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mourinho kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng Martial nh\u01b0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Martial b\u1ecb gh\u1ebb l\u1ea1nh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Theo t\u1edd The Times, Mourinho v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Man United \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh t\u1ee5t Martial \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp. M\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a Martial c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u01b0 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Sanchez c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford, Martial m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111\u00fang 4 l\u1ea7n. Trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u. Anh m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 chu\u1ed7i 5 tr\u1eadn xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. Martial c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Premier League t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng Hai t\u1edbi nay.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhay-vao-cuoc-dua-gianh-hang-hot-premier-league-172-184020.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/21/mu-nhay-vao-cuoc-dua-gianh-hang-hot-premier-league.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhay-vao-cuoc-dua-gianh-hang-hot-premier-league-172-184020.html\">M.U nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng hot Premier League</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, Martial kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf n\u01a1i n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i nh\u01b0 Sanchez, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Martial c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. V\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c anh n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Martial s\u1ebd r\u1eddi v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i gia ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00f2m ng\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Juventus, Atletico Madrid, Paris Saint-Germain hay c\u1ea3 k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Martial. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa Martial v\u1edbi Mourinho kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd ra \u0111i ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 sao tr\u1ebb Martial: </strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bao-phap-he-lo-ngoi-sao-se-roi-mu-trong-he-toi-172-183971.html\">B\u00e1o Ph\u00e1p h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ebd r\u1eddi M.U trong h\u00e8 t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-gui-psg-pogba-martial-neymar-172-183797.html\">MU g\u1eedi PSG: Pogba + Martial = Neymar?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-hy-sinh-sao-khung-de-co-gareth-bale-172-183279.html\">M.U hy sinh sao kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Gareth Bale?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dau-hieu-cho-thay-martial-se-roi-mu-he-nay-172-183063.html\">D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Martial s\u1ebd r\u1eddi MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tien-dao-martial-roi-mu-sau-mua-nay-172-182457.html\">Martial ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U sau m\u00f9a n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/martial-muon-dao-tau-khoi-mu-172-182219.html\">Ch\u00e1n c\u1ea3nh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, Martial mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Seria A</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2015/10/30/rebongmartial30102015.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><br>\r\n<strong>Video t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb Martial trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o MU:</strong><br>\r\n<img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1037","checkdouble":"184019"},{"date":"15:09 11/04","title":"M.U nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh \"h\u00e0ng hot\" Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/10/21/mu-nhay-vao-cuoc-dua-gianh-hang-hot-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom