g_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Theo Sky Sports News, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Richarlison c\u1ee7a Watford. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n MU mua Richarlison \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Richarlison</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Richarlison l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Watford \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 31 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuc soc MU mua Richarlison voi gia sieu khung hinh anh\" title=\"C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c MU mua Richarlison v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/26/Cuc-soc-MU-mua-Richarlison-voi-gia-sieu-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Richarlison \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Watford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1997 r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c trung phong c\u1eafm. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t gi\u00fap Richarlison tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-gap-kho-trong-thuong-vu-chieu-mo-sao-watford-172-178646.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Richarlison</strong></span>, BL\u0110 The Blues \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Arsenal v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Watford. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/watford-chot-gia-ban-hang-hot-richarlison-172-183879.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Watford ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Richarlison</strong></span>, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Watford \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, Chelsea, Arsenal ho\u1eb7c PSG s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nM.U gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Richarlison</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sky Sports News, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Richarlison c\u1ee7a Watford. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n MU mua Richarlison \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuc soc MU mua Richarlison voi gia sieu khung hinh anh 2\" title=\"C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c MU mua Richarlison v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/21/mu-nhay-vao-cuoc-dua-gianh-hang-hot-premier-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mua Richarlison \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nMourinho mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a n\u0103ng v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Richarlison v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Watford y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/manchester-united-1.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>M.U</strong></span> chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb dao \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Richarlison \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League, b\u1edfi v\u1eady M.U ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf Old Trafford s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Richarlison \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/992069-40942/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Richarlison \u1edf Premier League 2017/18<br>\r\n</span><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1036","checkdouble":"184020"},{"date":"09:09 11/04","title":"CLB TP.HCM t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng khi m\u1ea5t \"Ronaldo Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/clb-tphcm-ton-that-nang-khi-phi-son-chan-thuong-nghi-mot-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}