o trung t\u00e2m trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB TPHCM ton that nang khi Phi Son chan thuong nghi mot thang hinh anh\" title=\"CLB TPHCM t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng khi Phi S\u01a1n ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/clb-tphcm-ton-that-nang-khi-phi-son-chan-thuong-nghi-mot-thang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Tr\u1ea7n Phi S\u01a1n ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 1 th\u00e1ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau b\u1ed1n v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, Phi S\u01a1n c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh khi ghi 2 trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 3 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a CLB TP.HCM m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Phi S\u01a1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch C\u00f4ng Vinh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u00e0 Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a BVN.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Phi S\u01a1n ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua SLNA v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9 v\u00f2ng 1 V-League 2018, CLB TP.HCM c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn th\u00eam t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t khi Phi S\u01a1n ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Theo ch\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, anh b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t kho\u1ea3ng 1 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phi S\u01a1n c\u0169ng b\u1ed9c b\u1ea1ch v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n Bongdaplus: \"S\u1ed1 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111en. \u0110ang phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00ec l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng may d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Theo ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u1ef9, t\u00f4i b\u1ecb r\u00e1ch d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t 3-4 tu\u1ea7n m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i xem c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. Hy v\u1ecdng, anh em s\u1ebd \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t \u1edf ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia, CLB TP.HCM c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ed3ng Th\u00e1p. Trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/bang-xep-hang-25.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">BXH V-League 2018</span></span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Tr\u1ea7n Phi S\u01a1n:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-toshiya-miura-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-slna-291-183609.html\">HLV Toshiya Miura sau tr\u1eadn thua SLNA: Th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf Phi S\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/tphcm-vs-slna-19h00-ngay-54-tam-diem-phi-son-291-183557.html\">TPHCM vs SLNA (19h00 ng\u00e0y 5/4): T\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m Phi S\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tphcm-10-khanh-hoa-phi-son-tiep-tuc-mang-ve-niem-vui-cho-thay-miura-168-183335.html\">TPHCM 1-0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a: Phi S\u01a1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mang v\u1ec1 ni\u1ec1m vui cho th\u1ea7y Miura</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sai-gon-12-tphcm-lan-dau-cua-hlv-miura-tai-vleague-168-182629.html\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 1-2 TPHCM: L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Miura t\u1ea1i V-League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-phi-son-vu-minh-tuan-co-ben-do-moi-o-vleague-2018-168-176800.html\">Sau Phi S\u01a1n, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t V\u0169 Minh Tu\u1ea5n c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi \u1edf V-League 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/clb-tphcm-chot-ngay-ra-mat-hlv-miura-va-phi-son-168-176790.html\">CLB TP.HCM ch\u1ed1t ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft HLV Miura v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Phi S\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1035","checkdouble":"184000"},{"date":"10:09 11/04","title":"B\u1ea5u T\u00fa kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi gh\u1ebf T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c VPF","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/bau-tu-khang-dinh-se-rut-khoi-ghe-tong-giam-doc-vpf.jpeg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf