ackground-position:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn ch\u1ecbu \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 5 V-League 2018 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/tong-hop-ha-noi-50-hagl-vong-3-vleague-2018-325-183599.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 5-0 HAGL</span></span> khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c thi\u1ec7t \u0111\u01a1n thi\u1ec7t k\u00e9p. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u1eadm, HAGL c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. C\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t v\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/an-the-do-truc-tiep-cau-thu-hagl-nhan-an-phat-cuc-nang-291-183608.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">\u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c</span></span>.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL cua bau Duc co su thay doi nhan su o phut cuoi khi Van Toan the cho Duc Luong trong danh sach dang ky thi dau.\" title=\"HAGL c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i khi V\u0103n To\u00e0n th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 \u0110\u1ee9c L\u01b0\u01a1ng trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/ngoai-tang-tien-mot-loat-cau-thu-hagl-nghi-thi-dau-o-vong-5-vleague-2018.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>M\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 5 V-League 2018.</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i Duy M\u1ea1nh b\u00ean ph\u00eda H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. Chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khi\u1ebfn HAGL kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady trong hi\u1ec7p hai. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea5m T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>M\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ba c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo l\u00e0 Ch\u00e2u Ng\u1ecdc Quang, A Ho\u00e0ng v\u00e0 L\u00ea \u0110\u1ee9c L\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ch\u00e2u Ng\u1ecdc Quang c\u00f3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i ra s\u00e2n s\u1edbm nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y b\u1ecb d\u00e3n d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ngh\u1ec9 4 tu\u1ea7n.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">A Ho\u00e0ng d\u00f9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn n\u00e9n \u0111au ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a HAGL sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm. M\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 L\u00ea \u0110\u1ee9c L\u01b0\u01a1ng khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf c\u01a1 h\u00e1ng. Vi\u1ec7c m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi\u1ebfn HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 HAGL v\u1eeba th\u1eafng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 5-0, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e2m l\u00fd. Trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/bang-xep-hang-25.html\" target=\"_blank\">BXH V-League 2018</span>, HAGL \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 ch\u00edn v\u1edbi 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau b\u1ed1n v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam c\u00e1c tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 HAGL:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/clb-ha-noi-mat-la-chan-thep-o-vong-5-vleague-168-183952.html\">CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u1ea5t &ldquo;l\u00e1 ch\u1eafn th\u00e9p&rdquo; \u1edf v\u00f2ng 5 V-League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bau-tu-tang-tien-khong-lo-chuyen-phai-boi-thuong-cho-duy-manh-168-183947.html\">B\u1ea7u T\u00fa: T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng lo chuy\u1ec7n ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng cho Duy M\u1ea1nh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-than-quang-ninh-ly-giai-ve-that-bai-bat-ngo-truoc-clb-hagl-168-183901.html\">HLV Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB HAGL</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-tung-bung-50-truoc-quang-ninh-168-183900.html\">HLV HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 5-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ban-ky-luat-vff-ra-an-phat-cho-trung-ve-tang-tien-cua-hagl-168-183873.html\">Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho trung v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a HAGL</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-17h00-ngay-94-cup-quoc-gia-2018-372-183871.html\">HAGL 5-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (KT): \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u1edf c\u00fap QG</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1033","checkdouble":"184007"},{"date":"11:13 11/04","title":"\u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-8 Australia: HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung ch\u1ec9 ra nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/11/dt-nu-viet-nam-thua-australia-hlv-mai-duc-chung-chi-ra-nguyen-nhan.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlere