color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam thua Australia v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 0-8, HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam thua to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o VCK b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng nh\u1eb1m gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 World Cup 2019. Theo \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1ec7, hai \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed7i b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u1ef1 World Cup, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 play-off \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT nu Viet Nam thua Australia, HLV Mai Duc Chung chi nguyen nhan hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam thua Australia, HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung ch\u1ec9 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/dt-nu-viet-nam-thua-australia-hlv-mai-duc-chung-chi-ra-nguyen-nhan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><strong>HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung ch\u1ec9 ra nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam thua Australia v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-8.</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 World Cup r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf. Sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-vo-dich-chau-a-2018-nu-viet-nam-thua-dam-nhat-ban-168-183781.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-4</span></span>, \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam thua Australia v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 0-8, qua \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng n\u1eef H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam thua Australia</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng thua to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7: \"Ch\u00fang ta thua Australia v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 thua to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ef9 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin, c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb hai th\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ecd x\u00e1t, h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i nam nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0. C\u00f2n hai tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb th\u00f4i, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Australia\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video-bong-da-viet-nam/tong-hop-nu-viet-nam-08-nu-australia-vck-chau-a-2018-325-184008.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">\u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam thua Australia</span></span> khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 ba h\u1eb9p l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0ng m\u00e0 s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng gi\u1eefa \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 16h45 ng\u00e0y 13/4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam c\u00e1c tin kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-vo-dich-chau-a-2018-nu-viet-nam-thua-dam-nhat-ban-168-183781.html\">VCK v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018: N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam thua \u0111\u1eadm Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-nu-viet-nam-04-nu-nhat-ban-vck-chau-a-2018-325-183761.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-4 N\u1eef Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (VCK ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-nu-viet-nam-dat-chan-toi-jordan-de-chuan-bi-cho-giac-mo-world-cup-168-183444.html\">\u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n t\u1edbi Jordan \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-cu-cua-bong-da-viet-nam-tiet-lo-vu-khi-dang-so-cua-jordan-168-182956.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u0169 kh\u00ed \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Jordan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-nu-viet-nam-duoc-tiep-lua-trong-ngay-dau-xuan-168-180665.html\">\u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp l\u1eeda trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u xu\u00e2n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-nu-viet-nam-tap-huan-cang-ngay-sau-tet-nguyen-dan-168-180544.html\">\u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n c\u0103ng ngay sau T\u1ebft Nguy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1032","checkdouble":"184011"},{"date":"09:48 11/04","title":"H\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p Man City, Lovren v\u1eabn e s\u1ee3 1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/danh-bai-ca-man-city-lovren-van-e-so-1-doi-thu-o-ban-ket-c1.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-c