50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Dejan Lovren ng\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Real Madrid \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League d\u00f9 L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eeba san ph\u1eb3ng s\u00e2n Etihad v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Man City v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c l\u00e0 5-1.</h2>\r\n<h2>Liverpool c\u00f9ng Roma s\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League sau <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-man-city-vs-liverpool-01h45-ngay-114-champions-league-201718-372-183965.html\" target=\"_blank\">chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Etihad</span> c\u1ee7a Man City v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam qua. Roma c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0nh cho 4 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t sau khi l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal Madrid h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League sau khi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 3-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Juventus h\u1ed3i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Bayern Munich c\u0169ng \u0111ang n\u1eafm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn khi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Sevilla.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung ve Lovren ngai phai gap Real o ban ket Champions League hinh anh\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Lovren ng\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Real \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/danh-bai-ca-man-city-lovren-van-e-so-1-doi-thu-o-ban-ket-c1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lovren ng\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Real \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lovren e ng\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 4 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft n\u0103m nay, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Bayern c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm nh\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng trung v\u1ec7 Lovren v\u1eabn e s\u1ee3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Real Madrid h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n v\u00ec s\u1ef1 gi\u00e0 d\u01a1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cB\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c ri\u00eang. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Real Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi b\u1ea1n so s\u00e1nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Bayern ho\u1eb7c Roma. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft l\u00e0 Real Madrid\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tranh-cai-tran-man-city-12-liverpool-leroy-sane-da-viet-vi-hay-chua-184-183975.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/tranh-cai-tran-man-city-12-liverpool-leroy-sane-da-viet-vi-hay-chua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tranh-cai-tran-man-city-12-liverpool-leroy-sane-da-viet-vi-hay-chua-184-183975.html\">Tranh c\u00e3i tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool: Leroy Sane \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb hay ch\u01b0a?</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool trong s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00e1o xanh c\u0169ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Liverpool c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. H\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng l\u00ec l\u1ee3m trong c\u1ea3 hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Man City \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Liverpool c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng cho \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1eeba qua, The Kop b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi may m\u1eafn, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1eeda \u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Etihad v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Liverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ha-guc-man-city-liverpool-ha-not-man-utd-184-183978.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Champions League</span> (33 b\u00e0n), v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man United (32 b\u00e0n m\u00f9a 2002/03).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-hung-salah-noi-gi-sau-khi-giai-cuu-liverpool-o-etihad-184-183990.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Salah n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Liverpool \u1edf Etihad?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/mane-liverpool-co-the-danh-bai-bat-ky-doi-bong-nao-184-183989.html\">Mane: Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-man-city-12-liverpool-184-183983.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/klopp-chang-so-gi-ban-thang-som-cua-man-city-het-184-183981.html\">Klopp: Ch\u1eb3ng s\u1ee3 g\u00ec b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm c\u1ee7a Man City h\u1ebft!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/bi-loai-xung-dang-khoi-c1-pep-van-trut-gian-len-trong-tai-184-183980.html\">B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfi C1, Pep v\