x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Man City 2-1, HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u Champions c\u00f9ng CLB Roma.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Liverpool x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Liverpool thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 nh\u00e0n nh\u00e3 v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam qua. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c \u00e9p kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng 1 l\u1ea7n. B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, Mo Salah v\u00e0 Roberto Firmino \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 2-1 (5-1 chung cu\u1ed9c), \u0111\u01b0a Liverpool v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Jurgen Klopp cho bi\u1ebft: <em>&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Man City l\u00e0 CLB m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd. <strong>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y.</strong></em><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;Cho \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho t\u1eebng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 ai.&rdquo;</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Man City\" title=\"Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/lot-vao-ban-ket-c1-liverpool-san-bang-ky-luc-an-tuong-cua-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Man City trong c\u1ea3 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh, c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. Trong v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng qua, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y t\u1ed1t l\u00e0nh ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai, r\u1ed3i thua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu n\u1ebfu x\u1ea5u tr\u1eddi, \u0111\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1i v\u1eady. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua&rdquo;</em> &ndash; Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ed1c v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a Roma<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;C\u00e1i qu\u00e1i g\u00ec v\u1eady?&quot;</em> HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecf ra ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean. <em>&quot;H\u1ecd m\u1ea5t Salah v\u00e0 v\u1eabn v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n k\u1ebft?</em> <em>Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi t\u00f4i b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean c\u1ea7u thang v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ai \u0111\u00f3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o Roma \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00f9a. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng Roma, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi Edin Dzeko. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i.&rdquo;</em><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, to\u00e0n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mong \u0111\u1ee3i. Champions League r\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ngh\u0129 Man City v\u00e0 Barca s\u1ebd v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn xem, l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.&rdquo;</em><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft: <em>&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u00f3 2 CLB m\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c c\u00f9ng Liverpool v\u00e0 Roma. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1edd xem \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra.&rdquo;</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tieu-diet-man-city-salah-lai-duoc-so-sanh-voi-messi-184-184005.html\">Ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Man City, Salah l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/danh-bai-ca-man-city-lovren-van-e-so-1-doi-thu-o-ban-ket-c1-184-184003.html\">H\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p Man City, Lovren v\u1eabn e s\u1ee3 1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/gabriel-jesus-man-city-da-khoi-dau-tot-nhung-184-183996.html\">Gabriel Jesus: Man City \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-nhan-man-city-12-liverpool-184-183991.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn n\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn Man City 1-2 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/mane-liverpool-co-the-danh-bai-bat-ky-doi-bong-nao-184-183989.html\">Mane: Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1030","checkdouble":"184004"},{"date":"10:22 11/04","title":"Ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Man City, Salah l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/tieu-diet-man-city-salah-lai-duoc-so-sanh-voi-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Reg