x}.ui-icon-grip-diagonal-se{background-position:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Frank Lampard so s\u00e1nh Salah v\u1edbi Messi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec9nh cao sau khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 39 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Liverpool h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Man City ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Etihad.</h2>\r\n<h2>M\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng quen thu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a Salah</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Salah \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 39 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Klopp v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Man City v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng. B\u1edfi Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPha ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Salah c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u1edf m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ph\u00fat 56 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7p hai m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a anh coi nh\u01b0 v\u00f9i d\u1eadp to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u00fd ch\u00ed chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a The Citizens. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf ph\u00fat 77 c\u1ee7a Firmino.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tieu diet Man City, Salah duoc so sanh voi Messi hinh anh\" title=\"Ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Man City, Salah \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/tieu-diet-man-city-salah-lai-duoc-so-sanh-voi-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Salah \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Messi sau m\u00e0n h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1eeb h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Chelsea t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i Anfield</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Frank Lampard t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Salah t\u1ea1i Chelsea trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian 18 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. Nh\u01b0ng khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Salah \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng c\u01a1n ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 sau <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-man-city-vs-liverpool-01h45-ngay-114-champions-league-201718-372-183965.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i Etihad</span> v\u1eeba qua, Lampard kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i Salah v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng so s\u00e1nh ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi hi\u1ec7n nay.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tranh-cai-tran-man-city-12-liverpool-leroy-sane-da-viet-vi-hay-chua-184-183975.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/tranh-cai-tran-man-city-12-liverpool-leroy-sane-da-viet-vi-hay-chua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tranh-cai-tran-man-city-12-liverpool-leroy-sane-da-viet-vi-hay-chua-184-183975.html\">Tranh c\u00e3i tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool: Leroy Sane \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb hay ch\u01b0a?</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn Man City 1-2 Liverpool trong s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00e1o xanh c\u0169ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u1ede Chelsea, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi Chelsea khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc l\u00e0 Eden Hazard. So v\u1edbi Salah, Hazard c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t m\u00ecnh kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh, Salah \u0111\u00e3 cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 duy xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Lionel Messi r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. V\u00e0 Salah c\u0169ng \u0111ang b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u00f4i khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n nh\u01b0ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</em><strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u1ec1 c\u1ed7 m\u00e1y ghi b\u00e0n Salah:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-hung-salah-noi-gi-sau-khi-giai-cuu-liverpool-o-etihad-184-183990.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Salah n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Liverpool \u1edf Etihad?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-liverpool-salah-da-thuc-su-la-cau-thu-dang-cap-the-gioi-172-183960.html\">G\u00f3c Liverpool: Salah \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/kane-tuyen-chien-salah-trong-cuoc-dua-vua-pha-luoi-172-183860.html\">Kane tuy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn Salah trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mohamed-salah-va-kevin-de-bruyne-ai-xung-dang-xuat-sac-nhat-premier-league-201718-172-183806.html\">Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Kevin De Bruyne: Ai x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League 2017/18?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/khong-phai-salah-day-moi-la-nguoi-hung-thuc-su-cua-liverpool-184-183736.html\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Salah, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-liverpool-tin-salah-se-vuon-ngang-tam-ronaldo-messi-172-183630.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Liverpool tin Salah s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u01a1n ngang t\u1ea7m Ronaldo, Messi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1029","checkdouble":"184005"}]}